  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients scheduled for decompression and posterior thoracic and/or lumbar instrumented
             spinal fusion because of spinal metastasis/metastases.

          -  Informed signed consent.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Contrast fluid allergy.

          -  Clotting disorders.

          -  Renal failure.

          -  Not suitable for arterial access.

          -  Pregnancy.
      </textblock>
